Log-in into the Gerrit instance you want to commit into. Go into 'Projects', list, then choose the repo you want to make the change in: 
[INDENT][IMG="gerrit project select"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363174[/IMG][/INDENT]
Hit the 'Create Change' button: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit CreateButton"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363248[/IMG][/INDENT]
This open a popup asking for some information: 
[LIST]
[*][I]Select branch for new change[/I]: the branch you want to commit in, 
[*][I]Enter topic for new change[/I]: leave empty
[*][I]Description[/I]: Enter commit message
[/LIST]
Finally hit [I]Create[/I]
[INDENT][IMG="fillchange"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363249[/IMG][/INDENT]

Now your change page is open, you can start editing files with the [I]Edit[/I] button on the right: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit Edit Buton"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363257[/IMG][/INDENT]
then [I]Add[/I] the file you want change: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit Add file"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363259[/IMG][/INDENT]
The file open in an editor, make the needed changes and save with [I]Save[/I] button, then [I]Close[/I]: 
(Redo the step if you need to change multiples files.)
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit editor"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363261[/IMG][/INDENT]
When all your changes are present, hit the [I]Done Editing[/I] button to validate your changes. 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit done edit"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363264[/IMG][/INDENT]
Your changes are pending and you can display it while clicking on file name: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit done editing"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363266[/IMG][/INDENT]
The changed section is highlighted. If you made a mistake you can use the [IMG="pencil"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363274[/IMG] icon: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit check edit"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363272[/IMG][/INDENT]
Use the [IMG]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363276[/IMG] button to get back on the summary page. 
[B]WARNING[/B]: your change is only a draft for now, you need to publish it: 
[INDENT][IMG="Gerrit publish edit"]https://forum.xda-developers.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=4363277[/IMG][/INDENT]
